    "rich_text_tnPcKU": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_UaEgWd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Korean Beauty, Refined.",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_bHYQkg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>What does \"CHALTTOK\" mean?</h2><p>In Korea, when two things fit together flawlessly—like a key in a lock, or two soulmates meeting for the first time—we use the expression \"It's Chalttok\" (찰떡).</p><p>It means a \"<strong>Perfect Match</strong>.\"</p><p>We named our brand <strong>CHALTTOK</strong> because we believe skincare shouldn't be a guessing game. It should be a perfect fit for your life, your routine, and your skin's unique needs. We are dedicated to creating products that feel like they were made just for you—products that adhere to your skin perfectly and deliver results seamlessly.</p><h2>Mission & Vision</h2><p><strong>Finding Your Chemistry</strong> At CHALTTOK, we obsess over the \"chemistry\" between ingredients and your skin. We don't just follow trends; we study what truly works. We combine Korea’s advanced skincare technology with a philosophy of balance to create brands that stick with you.</p><p><strong>Introducing Our First Collection</strong>: Sarang Our journey begins with Sarang, a serum line inspired by the most powerful force of all—Love. Under the CHALTTOK umbrella, we will continue to introduce curated collections that serve as the perfect answer to your skin's questions.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
